rows.label: tlk45400071_02_msg0001
rows.name:
So I hear Superbia and Invidia
are finally making peace.

rows.label: tlk45400071_02_msg0002
rows.name:
No more war is a good thing, but
I don't know what Superbia is
going to do from here on out.

rows.label: tlk45400071_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Everyone knows the homeland isn't going
to last much longer. Is Superbia just
going to perish with its Divine Beast?

rows.label: tlk45400071_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Oh, it's no good, I'm just depressing
myself thinking about it. I'll go grab
a pick-me-up Odifa at Cafe Lutino.
